"engines":"","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"TV"},{"label":"Internet"},{"label":"DVD Player"}],"toys":[{"label":"Fishing Equipment"},{"label":"Jet Ski"},{"label":"Paddle Board"},{"label":"Wake Board"},{"label":"Water Ski"},{"label":"Knee Board"},{"label":"Wind Surf"},{"label":"Snorkeling Equipment"}],"entertainment":["Internet","TV","DVD Player"],"tenders":[]},"crew":[{"name":"MICHAEL MATHIAS","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7580644139::vessel::d5cc23cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::73acb520-1ced-11ef-8b60-c9be471191a8.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Born in Johannesburg , South Africa, Captain\nMikey has always had a passion for yachting. His\nlove for the ocean is unmatched and in his off-\ntime you can catch him fishing. While being a\ncertified captain, Mikey also has experience in\nbartending and can whip up almost any cocktail.\nNever without a smile, Captain Mikey will do his\nutmost to ensure you have the charter of a\nlifetime."},{"name":"SONER KIREMIT","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7580644139::vessel::d5cc23cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::86fd9f90-1ced-11ef-8b60-c9be471191a8.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Bodrum born, Soner Kiremit is Beyaz Lale\ntreasured deckhand. He is not only extremely\nhard working but takes immense pride in what he\ndoes. Soner passions are on the water and is a\npro when it comes to water sport activities. He is\nalways willing to lend a helping hand."},{"name":"IRAZ SEZGI","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7580644139::vessel::d5cc23cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a36f6c30-1ced-11ef-8b60-c9be471191a8.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Iraz, our versatile chef, brings a rich background to Beyaz\nLale. Born in Istanbul and raised along the Bosphorus,\nshe discovered her love for cooking early on. After\nexploring roles in diving, seamanship, and archeology,\nshe pursued her passion for cuisine, training at Foodrum\nin Bodrum. With a love for reading, sailing, swimming,\nand traveling, Iraz infuses her dishes with creativity and\ndepth. Her diverse experiences ensure every meal is a\nculinary adventure for our guests."},{"name":"Gülsen Ozdemir","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7580644139::vessel::d5cc23cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c58e5100-1ced-11ef-8b60-c9be471191a8.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Gülsen, a seasoned yacht stewardess with five years of\nexperience, joins Beyaz Lale with a passion for the sea\nand a dedication to exceptional service. Her joy for life\nand love of the ocean make her a perfect fit for our\ncrew. Gülsen delights in creating unforgettable\nmemories for guests, always with a warm smile and a\ncommitment to making their experience seamless and\nenjoyable."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":1900000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":1900000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":2300000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2300000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"May - October","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":1900000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":1900000,"amount":1900000,"conditions":"","taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.2}}],"total":2280000,"subTotal":1900000,"totalTax":380000},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Greece","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Greece"],"coordinates":[24.261736188816826,38.42232351533858],"bbox":[19.646484375,34.934472656249994,28.231835937500023,41.743798828124994]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"June - September","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-06-01T00:00:00.00